h the price. Oh another really cool thing with all the restarting I've done...not one single game was the same. Not even remotely. It's a mystery bag full of twisted fun. I highly recommend this game for those that like a good challenge, are willing to work with the issues knowing they are being fixed as FAST as the Dev's can and are a bit twisted...liking and/or loving Lovecraft is just a really awesome perk."
