oys down the road, and I cannot wait for it.  I paid because I want to help them make this game better, so I and others can enjoy it.  I paid because I belive in that kooky colonial  dream, and I want to ride this crazy train where-ever it may go!So rather than pout because it's not perfect, put on your big kid underoos, and grab your gear, it's Colonial  time!Tell the devs the issues and thell try to solve it, or explain why it's an inteded effect rather than a seemingly random thing."
