olutely nothing. It is steampunk fanfiction visualised into some kind of bizarre abomination of a computer program.First I thought it might end up as a finished product, since the developers are so dedicated and obviously invested time and money into this. I get the feeling they put their heart and soul into this too. Sadly they built the foundation of their dream on top of quicksand, so no matter how much they work on this - it will inevitably sink down into the depths."
